<section class="science">
  <div class="science-header">
    <span class="caption">WISSEN</span>
    <h2 class="science-heading">Zwischen Forschung und Markt</h2>
    <p class="science-text">
      Wir verbinden wissenschaftliche Erkenntnisse mit der Praxis des
      Kaffeeanbaus. In unseren Artikeln teilen wir neue Erkenntnisse und
      Perspektiven aus unserer Arbeit.
    </p>
    <a href="/wissen" class="science-link">Zu den Artikeln ›</a>
  </div>
  <div class="science-cards">
    <article class="science-card">
      <span class="caption">Knowledge & Science</span>
      <div class="card-image"></div>
      <h4 class="card-title">Article Headline</h4>
      <p class="card-subtitle">Article Subline</p>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-tertiary">
          <span>Tertiary Button</span>
          <svg class="arrow" width="14" height="11" viewBox="0 0 14 11" fill="none">
            <path d="M1 5.5h12m0 0L8.5 1M13 5.5L8.5 10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <div class="card-meta">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="10" stroke="#e3e2e0" stroke-width="1"/>
            <path d="M11 6v5l3 3" stroke="#e3e2e0" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
          <span>6 Min</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
